### 1. Get all existing measurements
GET http://localhost:8080/rest/measurements
Accept: application/json

### 2. Create Record 1 (Felix)
POST http://localhost:8080/rest/measurements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "01.12.2025",
  "user": "felix",
  "height": 180.0,
  "weight": 80.0
}

